#

Lemon-Dill Shrimp Chowder

$15.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-Carb

Tags:

SeafoodComfort FoodChowder

Description

A creamy, zesty chowder featuring succulent shrimp and sweet corn, perfect for a cozy dinner.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 lb
  • Sweet corn (fresh or frozen): 1 cup
  • Potatoes (diced): 2 medium
  • Onion (chopped): 1 medium
  • Garlic (minced): 3 cloves
  • Chicken broth: 4 cups
  • Heavy cream: 1 cup
  • Dill (fresh, chopped): 2 tbsp
  • Lemon juice: 2 tbsp
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt and pepper: to taste
